into a she-camel's vulva,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Umawee, S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that she may think it to be her young one, [when it is taken forth,] and incline to it, [and therefore yield her milk;] like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"durojap","text_ar":"دُرْجَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (El-Umawee, S.)       -A3-  A thing, or an event,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that comes before its time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"season:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) that which comes in its time, or season, is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wazomN","text_ar":"وَزْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n5750","headword_ar":"جِزْمٌ","root":"jzm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A portion, share,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) of palmtrees (TA) [and app. of the fruit of a palm-tree, &c.: see 1, third sentence]."}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]}]}}